<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Batch and mass payouts are available for distributed teams and large recipient groups.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">The platform includes a dual-workspace model, with a B2B workspace for the company and a B2C workspace for recipients through Coinhold by EMCD.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">OTC support is available for selected crypto-to-fiat, crypto-to-crypto, and cash exchange cases, subject to corporate verification and KYC/AML review.</span></li>
